      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
      "name": "Lower Spears!",
      "sort": 600000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> to <span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The skeletons engage in a coordinated longspear attack against each enemy within @Template[type:emanation|distance:10]{10 feet} (@Check[type:reflex|dc:27|basic:true] save). The damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> [[/r {2d8}[piercing]]]{2d8 piercing damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> [[/r {3d8+8}[piercing]]]{3d8+8 piercing damage}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> [[/r {4d8+8}[piercing]]]{4d8+8 piercing damage}</p>"
