      "sort": 700000,
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The infantry is in a phalanx</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The skeletons lower their longspears and charge. The troop Strides in a straight line until they're adjacent to an enemy then use Lower Spears!, dealing [[/r {3d8+8}[piercing]]]{3d8+8 piercing damage}. Any creature that fails its save is also knocked @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.j91X7x0XSomq8d60]{Prone}.</p>"
